{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some components can be used for "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indicators"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/indicators"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Badge","text":"Badge"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"title":"Orange","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_badge_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_badge_OrangeCompact"}]}],"title":"Orange Compact"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_badge_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"title":"Sosh"},{"title":"Wireframe","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_badge_Wireframe","type":"image"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge"},{"text":" is a small UI element used to highlight status, notifications, or categorization within an interface. It is often displayed as a label or indicator with a distinct background color and text.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"tabs":[{"title":"SwiftUI","content":[{"code":["    \/\/ Info badge in medium size without information","    OUDSBadge(status: .info, size: .medium)","","    \/\/ Negative badge in medium size with count information","    OUDSBadge(count: 1, status: .negative, size: .medium)","","    \/\/ Neutral badge in medium size with an image","    OUDSBadge(status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")), accessibilityLabel: \"Like\", size: .medium)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"level":3,"text":"Tag","anchor":"Tag","type":"heading"},{"tabs":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"title":"Orange"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"title":"Orange Compact"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"title":"Sosh"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe"}]}],"title":"Wireframe"}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category. It helps users quickly find, group, or understand content.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"content":[{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","\/\/ Or also","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","    ","\/\/ Tag with negative status with bullet","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .negative(leading: .bullet)","    ","\/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","\/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","\/\/ you can flip the icon","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","    ","\/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","    ","\/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"type":"codeListing"}],"title":"SwiftUI"}]},{"anchor":"Input-Tag","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Input Tag"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_inputTag_Orange"}]}],"title":"Orange"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_inputTag_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]}],"title":"Orange Compact"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_inputTag_Sosh","type":"image"}]}],"title":"Sosh"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_inputTag_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"title":"Wireframe"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInputTag","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category, which can be removed or changed on tap."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Create an input tag","OUDSInputTag(\"Label\") {","    \/\/ Do something, usually remove itself from a list","}","    ","\/\/ Show in a list and remove when clicked","var names: [String] = [ \"Foo\", \"Bar\", \"Wizz\" ]","    ","ForEach(names, id: \\.self) { name in","    OUDSInputTag(label: name) {","        if let index = names.firstIndex(of: name) {","            names.remove(at: index)","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"title":"Indicators","images":[{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"card"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"kind":"article","references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documenta